<p>おれが<span class="vocab">椽鼻<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>椽鼻</rb><rt>えんばな</rt></ruby>&nbsp;edge of the veranda; edge of the porch</span></span>で<span class="vocab">清<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>清</rb><rt>きよ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Kiyo (name of Botchan's former maidservant)</span></span>の<span class="vocab">手紙<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>手紙</rb><rt>てがみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;letter</span></span>を<span class="vocab">ひらつかせながら<span class="vocabdef">ひらつかせながら&nbsp;while allowing to flutter (in the wind)</span></span>、<span class="vocab">考え込んでいる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>考</rb><rt>かんが</rt></ruby>え<ruby><rb>込</rb><rt>こ</rt></ruby>んでいる&nbsp;be lost in thought</span></span>と、しきりの<span class="vocab">襖<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>襖</rb><rt>ふすま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sliding partition</span></span>をあけて、<span class="vocab">萩野<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>萩野</rb><rt>はぎの</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Hagino (name of Botchan's landlord)</span></span>の<span class="vocab">お婆さん<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>婆</rb><rt>ばあ</rt></ruby>さん&nbsp;old woman</span></span>が<span class="vocab">晩めし<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>晩</rb><rt>ばん</rt></ruby>めし&nbsp;dinner</span></span>を<span class="vocab">持ってきた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>持</rb><rt>も</rt></ruby>ってきた&nbsp;brought</span></span>。まだ<span class="vocab">見てお出でる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>てお<ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>でる&nbsp;looking at; reading</span></span>のかなもし。えっぽど<span class="vocab">長い<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>長</rb><rt>なが</rt></ruby>い&nbsp;long; lengthy</span></span>お手紙じゃなもし、と<span class="vocab">云った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>云</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;said; remarked</span></span>から、ええ<span class="vocab">大事な<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大事</rb><rt>だいじ</rt></ruby>な&nbsp;important</span></span>手紙だから<span class="vocab">風<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>風</rb><rt>かぜ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;wind</span></span>に<span class="vocab">吹かして<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>吹</rb><rt>ふ</rt></ruby>かして&nbsp;be blown by</span></span>は見、吹かしては見るんだと、<span class="vocab">自分でも<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>自分</rb><rt>じぶん</rt></ruby>でも&nbsp;even to myself</span></span><span class="vocab">要領を得ない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>要領</rb><rt>ようりょう</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>得</rb><rt>え</rt></ruby>ない&nbsp;makes no sense</span></span><span class="vocab">返事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>返事</rb><rt>へんじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;response</span></span>をして<span class="vocab">膳についた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>膳</rb><rt>ぜん</rt></ruby>についた&nbsp;started dinner</span></span>。見ると<span class="vocab">今夜<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今夜</rb><rt>こんや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;tonight</span></span>も<span class="vocab">薩摩芋<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>薩摩芋</rb><rt>さつまいも</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sweet potato</span></span>の<span class="vocab">煮つけ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>煮</rb><rt>に</rt></ruby>つけ&nbsp;boiled with soy</span></span>だ。ここのうちは、<span class="vocab">いか銀<span class="vocabdef">いか<ruby><rb>銀</rb><rt>ぎん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Ikagin (name of Botchan's former landlord)</span></span>よりも<span class="vocab">鄭寧<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>鄭寧</rb><rt>ていねい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;polite; courteous</span></span>で、<span class="vocab">親切<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>親切</rb><rt>しんせつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;kind; considerate</span></span>で、しかも<span class="vocab">上品<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>上品</rb><rt>じょうひん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;refined; of good taste</span></span>だが、<span class="vocab">惜しい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>惜</rb><rt>お</rt></ruby>しい&nbsp;unfortunate; regretful</span></span><span class="vocab">事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fact; matter</span></span>に<span class="vocab">食い物<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>食</rb><rt>く</rt></ruby>い<ruby><rb>物</rb><rt>もの</rt></ruby>&nbsp;food</span></span>がまずい。<span class="vocab">昨日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>昨日</rb><rt>きのう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;yesterday</span></span>も<span class="vocab">芋<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>芋</rb><rt>いも</rt></ruby>&nbsp;potato</span></span><span class="vocab">一昨日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一昨日</rb><rt>おととい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the day before yesterday</span></span>も芋で今夜も芋だ。おれは芋は<span class="vocab">大好き<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大好</rb><rt>だいす</rt></ruby>き&nbsp;very fond of</span></span>だと<span class="vocab">明言した<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>明言</rb><rt>めいげん</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;declared; asserted</span></span><span class="vocab">には相違ない<span class="vocabdef">には<ruby><rb>相違</rb><rt>そうい</rt></ruby>ない&nbsp;without a doubt</span></span>が、こう<span class="vocab">立てつづけに<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>立</rb><rt>た</rt></ruby>てつづけに&nbsp;continually; in succession</span></span>芋を食わされては<span class="vocab">命<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>命</rb><rt>いのち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;life; existence</span></span>がつづかない。<span class="vocab">うらなり<span class="vocabdef">うらなり&nbsp;Uranari (nickname for Koga, the English teacher)</span></span><span class="vocab">君<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>くん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(suffix of familiarity for males)</span></span>を<span class="vocab">笑う<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>笑</rb><rt>わら</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;laugh at; joke about</span></span>どころか、おれ<span class="vocab">自身<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>自身</rb><rt>じしん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;myself</span></span>が<span class="vocab">遠からぬうちに<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>遠</rb><rt>とお</rt></ruby>からぬうちに&nbsp;in the not so distant future</span></span>、芋のうらなり<span class="vocab">先生<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>先生</rb><rt>せんせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;teacher</span></span>になっちまう。清ならこんな<span class="vocab">時<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>時</rb><rt>とき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;time; occasion</span></span>に、おれの好きな<span class="vocab">鮪<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>鮪</rb><rt>まぐろ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;bluefin tuna</span></span>の<span class="vocab">さし身<span class="vocabdef">さし<ruby><rb>身</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sashimi</span></span>か、<span class="vocab">蒲鉾<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>蒲鉾</rb><rt>かまぼこ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fish cake</span></span>の<span class="vocab">つけ焼<span class="vocabdef">つけ<ruby><rb>焼</rb><rt>やき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fish broiled with soy</span></span>を<span class="vocab">食わせる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>食</rb><rt>く</rt></ruby>わせる&nbsp;prepare food (for someone)</span></span>んだが、<span class="vocab">貧乏<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>貧乏</rb><rt>びんぼう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;impoverished</span></span><span class="vocab">士族<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>士族</rb><rt>しぞく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;samurai family</span></span>の<span class="vocab">けちん坊<span class="vocabdef">けちん<ruby><rb>坊</rb><rt>ぼう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;stinginess</span></span><span class="vocab">と来ちゃ<span class="vocabdef">と<ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>ちゃ&nbsp;when dealing with ...</span></span><span class="vocab">仕方がない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>仕方</rb><rt>しかた</rt></ruby>がない&nbsp;can't be helped</span></span>。どう考えても清といっしょでなくっちあ<span class="vocab">駄目<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>駄目</rb><rt>だめ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;no good; unacceptable</span></span>だ。もしあの<span class="vocab">学校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>学校</rb><rt>がっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;school</span></span>に長くでも<span class="vocab">居る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>居</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;be; remain (in a place)</span></span><span class="vocab">模様<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>模様</rb><rt>もよう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;indication; outlook</span></span>なら、<span class="vocab">東京<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>東京</rb><rt>とうきょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Tōkyō</span></span>から<span class="vocab">召び寄せて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>召</rb><rt>よ</rt></ruby>び<ruby><rb>寄</rb><rt>よ</rt></ruby>せて&nbsp;call (for someone)</span></span>やろう。<span class="vocab">天麩羅蕎麦<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>天麩羅蕎麦</rb><rt>てんぷらそば</rt></ruby>&nbsp;tempura soba</span></span>を<span class="vocab">食っちゃならない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>食</rb><rt>く</rt></ruby>っちゃならない&nbsp;not allowed to eat</span></span>、<span class="vocab">団子<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>団子</rb><rt>だんご</rt></ruby>&nbsp;dumplings</span></span>を食っちゃならない、それで<span class="vocab">下宿<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>下宿</rb><rt>げしゅく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;lodgings</span></span>に居て芋ばかり食って<span class="vocab">黄色く<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>黄色</rb><rt>きいろ</rt></ruby>く&nbsp;yellow</span></span>なっていろなんて、<span class="vocab">教育者<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教育者</rb><rt>きょういくしゃ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;educator</span></span>はつらいものだ。<span class="vocab">禅宗坊主<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>禅宗坊主</rb><rt>ぜんしゅうぼうず</rt></ruby>&nbsp;zen monk</span></span>だって、これよりは<span class="vocab">口<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>口</rb><rt>くち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;mouth</span></span>に<span class="vocab">栄耀<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>栄耀</rb><rt>えよう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;luxury</span></span>をさせているだろう。――おれは<span class="vocab">一皿<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一皿</rb><rt>ひとさら</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one plate</span></span>の芋を<span class="vocab">平げて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>平</rb><rt>たいら</rt></ruby>げて&nbsp;eat up</span></span>、<span class="vocab">机<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>机</rb><rt>つくえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;desk</span></span>の<span class="vocab">抽斗<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>抽斗</rb><rt>ひきだし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;drawer</span></span>から<span class="vocab">生卵<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生卵</rb><rt>なまたまご</rt></ruby>&nbsp;raw egg</span></span>を<span class="vocab">二つ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>二</rb><rt>ふた</rt></ruby>つ&nbsp;two (items; objects)</span></span><span class="vocab">出して<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>だ</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;take out</span></span>、<span class="vocab">茶碗<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>茶碗</rb><rt>ちゃわん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(rice) bowl; tea bowl</span></span>の<span class="vocab">縁<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>縁</rb><rt>ふち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;edge</span></span>で<span class="vocab">たたき割って<span class="vocabdef">たたき<ruby><rb>割</rb><rt>わ</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;crack apart (egg)</span></span>、ようやく<span class="vocab">凌いだ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>凌</rb><rt>しの</rt></ruby>いだ&nbsp;managed; endured</span></span>。生卵ででも<span class="vocab">営養<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>営養</rb><rt>えいよう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;nutrition ( usually <ruby><rb>栄養</rb><rt>えいよう</rt></ruby>)</span></span>をとらなくっちあ<span class="vocab">一週<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一週</rb><rt>いっしゅう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one week</span></span><span class="vocab">二十一時間<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>二十一時間</rb><rt>にじゅういちじかん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;twenty one hours</span></span>の<span class="vocab">授業<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>授業</rb><rt>じゅぎょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;class</span></span>が<span class="vocab">出来る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出来</rb><rt>でき</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;be possible</span></span>ものか。</p>

