<p><span class="vocab">今日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今日</rb><rt>きょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;today; this day</span></span>は<span class="vocab">清<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>清</rb><rt>きよ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Kiyo (name of Botchan's former maidservant)</span></span>の<span class="vocab">手紙<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>手紙</rb><rt>てがみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;letter</span></span>で<span class="vocab">湯に行く<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>湯</rb><rt>ゆ</rt></ruby>に<ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>く&nbsp;go to bathe</span></span><span class="vocab">時間<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>時間</rb><rt>じかん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;time</span></span>が<span class="vocab">遅くなった<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>遅</rb><rt>おそ</rt></ruby>くなった&nbsp;became late</span></span>。しかし<span class="vocab">毎日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>毎日</rb><rt>まいにち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;every day</span></span><span class="vocab">行きつけた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>きつけた&nbsp;visited; frequented</span></span>のを<span class="vocab">一日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一日</rb><rt>いちにち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one day</span></span>でも<span class="vocab">欠かす<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>欠</rb><rt>か</rt></ruby>かす&nbsp;miss; skip</span></span>のは<span class="vocab">心持ちがわるい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>心持</rb><rt>こころも</rt></ruby>ちがわるい&nbsp;doesn't feel right</span></span>。<span class="vocab">汽車<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>汽車</rb><rt>きしゃ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(steam) train</span></span>にでも<span class="vocab">乗って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>乗</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;ride; take (train, etc.)</span></span><span class="vocab">出懸けよう<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出懸</rb><rt>でか</rt></ruby>けよう&nbsp;set out (for)</span></span>と、<span class="vocab">例の<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>例</rb><rt>れい</rt></ruby>の&nbsp;the usual; the previously mentioned</span></span><span class="vocab">赤手拭<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>赤手拭</rb><rt>あかてぬぐい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;red towel</span></span>を<span class="vocab">ぶら下げて<span class="vocabdef">ぶら<ruby><rb>下</rb><rt>さ</rt></ruby>げて&nbsp;dangle</span></span><span class="vocab">停車場<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>停車場</rb><rt>ていしゃば</rt></ruby>&nbsp;stop; station</span></span>まで<span class="vocab">来る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>く</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;come (to)</span></span>と<span class="vocab">二三分前<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>二三分前</rb><rt>にさんぷんまえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;two or three minutes before</span></span>に<span class="vocab">発車<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>発車</rb><rt>はっしゃ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;departure (train, etc.)</span></span>したばかりで、<span class="vocab">少々<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>少々</rb><rt>しょうしょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;a bit</span></span><span class="vocab">待たなければならぬ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>待</rb><rt>ま</rt></ruby>たなければならぬ&nbsp;have to wait</span></span>。ベンチへ<span class="vocab">腰を懸けて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>腰</rb><rt>こし</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>懸</rb><rt>か</rt></ruby>けて&nbsp;sit down</span></span>、<span class="vocab">敷島<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>敷島</rb><rt>しきしま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Shikishima (cigarette brand)</span></span>を<span class="vocab">吹かして<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>吹</rb><rt>ふ</rt></ruby>かして&nbsp;smoke</span></span>いると、<span class="vocab">偶然<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>偶然</rb><rt>ぐうぜん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;by chance</span></span>にも<span class="vocab">うらなり<span class="vocabdef">うらなり&nbsp;Uranari (nickname for Koga, the English teacher)</span></span><span class="vocab">君<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>くん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(suffix of familiarity for males)</span></span>がやって来た。おれはさっきの<span class="vocab">話<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>話</rb><rt>はなし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;talk; story</span></span>を<span class="vocab">聞いて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>聞</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>いて&nbsp;hear</span></span>から、うらなり君がなおさら<span class="vocab">気の毒<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>気</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>毒</rb><rt>どく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;pitiable</span></span>になった。<span class="vocab">平常から<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>平常</rb><rt>ふだん</rt></ruby>から&nbsp;ordinarily; from habit</span></span><span class="vocab">天地の間<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>天地</rb><rt>てんち</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>間</rb><rt>あいだ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;between heaven and earth</span></span>に<span class="vocab">居候をしている<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>居候</rb><rt>いそうろう</rt></ruby>をしている&nbsp;be a burden; be a nuisance</span></span>ように、<span class="vocab">小さく<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>小</rb><rt>ちい</rt></ruby>さく&nbsp;meekly</span></span><span class="vocab">構えて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>構</rb><rt>かま</rt></ruby>えて&nbsp;position oneself; assume a posture</span></span>いるのがいかにも<span class="vocab">憐れ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>憐</rb><rt>あわ</rt></ruby>れ&nbsp;miserable</span></span>に<span class="vocab">見えた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>えた&nbsp;appeared</span></span>が、<span class="vocab">今夜<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今夜</rb><rt>こんや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;tonight</span></span>は<span class="vocab">憐れどころの騒ぎではない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>憐</rb><rt>あわ</rt></ruby>れどころの<ruby><rb>騒</rb><rt>さわ</rt></ruby>ぎではない&nbsp;'miserable' can't begin to describe it</span></span>。<span class="vocab">出来るならば<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出来</rb><rt>でき</rt></ruby>るならば&nbsp;if possible</span></span><span class="vocab">月給<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>月給</rb><rt>げっきゅう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(monthly) salary</span></span>を<span class="vocab">倍にして<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>倍</rb><rt>ばい</rt></ruby>にして&nbsp;double</span></span>、<span class="vocab">遠山<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>遠山</rb><rt>とおやま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Tōyama (family name of Madonna)</span></span>の<span class="vocab">お嬢さん<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>嬢</rb><rt>じょう</rt></ruby>さん&nbsp;young lady</span></span>と<span class="vocab">明日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>明日</rb><rt>あした</rt></ruby>&nbsp;tomorrow</span></span>から<span class="vocab">結婚<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>結婚</rb><rt>けっこん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;marriage</span></span>さして、<span class="vocab">一ヶ月<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一ヶ月</rb><rt>いっかげつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one month</span></span>ばかり<span class="vocab">東京<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>東京</rb><rt>とうきょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Tōkyō</span></span>へでも<span class="vocab">遊びに<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>遊</rb><rt>あそ</rt></ruby>びに&nbsp;for pleasure; as a tourist</span></span>やってやりたい<span class="vocab">気がした矢先<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>気</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>がした<ruby><rb>矢先</rb><rt>やさき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;at the point of feeling ...</span></span>だから、や<span class="vocab">お湯<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>湯</rb><rt>ゆ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;bath</span></span>ですか、さあ、こっちへ<span class="vocab">お懸けなさい<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>懸</rb><rt>か</rt></ruby>けなさい&nbsp;have a seat</span></span>と<span class="vocab">威勢よく<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>威勢</rb><rt>いせい</rt></ruby>よく&nbsp;gallantly</span></span><span class="vocab">席を譲る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>席</rb><rt>せき</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>譲</rb><rt>ゆず</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;make room (for someone) to sit</span></span>と、うらなり君は<span class="vocab">恐れ入った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>恐</rb><rt>おそ</rt></ruby>れ<ruby><rb>入</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;abashed; feeling small</span></span><span class="vocab">体裁<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>体裁</rb><rt>ていさい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;form; style</span></span>で、いえ<span class="vocab">構うておくれなさるな<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>構</rb><rt>かも</rt></ruby>うておくれなさるな&nbsp;don't trouble yourself (on my account)</span></span>、と<span class="vocab">遠慮<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>遠慮</rb><rt>えんりょ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;reserve; diffidence</span></span>だか<span class="vocab">何<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;what</span></span>だかやっぱり<span class="vocab">立ってる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>立</rb><rt>た</rt></ruby>ってる&nbsp;remain standing</span></span>。<span class="vocab">少し<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>少</rb><rt>すこ</rt></ruby>し&nbsp;a bit</span></span>待たなくっちゃ<span class="vocab">出ません<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>ません&nbsp;won't depart</span></span>、<span class="vocab">草臥れます<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>草臥</rb><rt>くたび</rt></ruby>れます&nbsp;get tired; be worn out</span></span>からお懸けなさいとまた<span class="vocab">勧めて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>勧</rb><rt>すす</rt></ruby>めて&nbsp;advise; offer</span></span>みた。<span class="vocab">実は<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>実</rb><rt>じつ</rt></ruby>は&nbsp;in fact; in truth</span></span>どうかして、そばへ懸けてもらいたかったくらいに気の毒でたまらない。それでは<span class="vocab">お邪魔を致しましょう<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>邪魔</rb><rt>じゃま</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>致</rb><rt>いた</rt></ruby>しましょう&nbsp;impose (on someone)</span></span>とようやくおれの<span class="vocab">云う<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>云</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;say; request</span></span><span class="vocab">事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;content; meaning</span></span>を聞いてくれた。<span class="vocab">世の中<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>世</rb><rt>よ</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>中</rb><rt>なか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the world</span></span>には<span class="vocab">野だ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>野</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>だ&nbsp;Noda (short for Nodaiko, nickname for Yoshikawa, the art teacher)</span></span>みたように<span class="vocab">生意気な<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生意気</rb><rt>なまいき</rt></ruby>な&nbsp;impudent; insolent</span></span>、<span class="vocab">出ないで済む<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>ないで<ruby><rb>済</rb><rt>す</rt></ruby>む&nbsp;be unwanted; be unneeded</span></span><span class="vocab">所<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>所</rb><rt>ところ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;place</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">必ず<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>必</rb><rt>かなら</rt></ruby>ず&nbsp;without fail</span></span><span class="vocab">顔を出す<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>顔</rb><rt>かお</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>だ</rt></ruby>す&nbsp;make an appearance; show one's face</span></span><span class="vocab">奴<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>奴</rb><rt>やつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fellow</span></span>もいる。<span class="vocab">山嵐<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>山嵐</rb><rt>やまあらし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Yama Arashi (nickname for Hotta, the head mathematics teacher)</span></span>のようにおれが<span class="vocab">居なくっちゃ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>居</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>なくっちゃ&nbsp;not be present; not be there</span></span><span class="vocab">日本<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>日本</rb><rt>にっぽん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Japan</span></span>が<span class="vocab">困る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>困</rb><rt>こま</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;have a difficult time; be at a loss</span></span>だろうと云うような<span class="vocab">面を肩の上へ載せてる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>面</rb><rt>つら</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>肩</rb><rt>かた</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>上</rb><rt>うえ</rt></ruby>へ<ruby><rb>載</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>せてる&nbsp;wear one's face like a badge of honor</span></span>奴もいる。そうかと<span class="vocab">思う<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;think</span></span>と、<span class="vocab">赤シャツ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>赤</rb><rt>あか</rt></ruby>シャツ&nbsp;Red Shirt (nickname for the head teacher)</span></span>のようにコスメチックと<span class="vocab">色男<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>色男</rb><rt>いろおとこ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;beau; lady-killer</span></span>の<span class="vocab">問屋<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>問屋</rb><rt>とんや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;wholesaler</span></span>をもって<span class="vocab">自ら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>自</rb><rt>みずか</rt></ruby>ら&nbsp;for oneself; on one's own initiative</span></span><span class="vocab">任じて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>任</rb><rt>にん</rt></ruby>じて&nbsp;appoint; nominate</span></span>いるのもある。<span class="vocab">教育<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教育</rb><rt>きょういく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;education</span></span>が<span class="vocab">生きて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>きて&nbsp;be alive</span></span>フロックコートを<span class="vocab">着れば<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>着</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>れば&nbsp;wear</span></span>おれになるんだと<span class="vocab">云わぬばかり<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>云</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>わぬばかり&nbsp;all but declaring</span></span>の<span class="vocab">狸<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>狸</rb><rt>たぬき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Tanuki (nickname for the school principal)</span></span>もいる。<span class="vocab">皆々<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>皆々</rb><rt>みなみな</rt></ruby>&nbsp;all; each one</span></span><span class="vocab">それ相応に<span class="vocabdef">それ<ruby><rb>相応</rb><rt>そうおう</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;in their respective ways</span></span><span class="vocab">威張ってる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>威張</rb><rt>いば</rt></ruby>ってる&nbsp;swagger; make one's importance felt</span></span>んだが、このうらなり<span class="vocab">先生<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>先生</rb><rt>せんせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;teacher</span></span>のように<span class="vocab">在れどもなきがごとく<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>在</rb><rt>あ</rt></ruby>れどもなきがごとく&nbsp;as if not existing</span></span>、<span class="vocab">人質に取られた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人質</rb><rt>ひとじち</rt></ruby>に<ruby><rb>取</rb><rt>と</rt></ruby>られた&nbsp;taken hostage; held for ransom</span></span><span class="vocab">人形<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人形</rb><rt>にんぎょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;puppet; figure</span></span>のように<span class="vocab">大人しく<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大人</rb><rt>おとな</rt></ruby>しく&nbsp;obediently; passively</span></span>しているのは見た事がない。顔はふくれているが、こんな<span class="vocab">結構な<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>結構</rb><rt>けっこう</rt></ruby>な&nbsp;fine; superb</span></span><span class="vocab">男<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>男</rb><rt>おとこ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;man</span></span>を<span class="vocab">捨てて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>捨</rb><rt>す</rt></ruby>てて&nbsp;discard; reject</span></span>赤シャツに<span class="vocab">靡く<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>靡</rb><rt>なび</rt></ruby>く&nbsp;yield to; be won over by</span></span>なんて、マドンナもよっぼど<span class="vocab">気の知れない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>気</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>知</rb><rt>し</rt></ruby>れない&nbsp;unfathomable; beyond understanding</span></span><span class="vocab">おきゃん<span class="vocabdef">おきゃん&nbsp;hussy; minx</span></span>だ。赤シャツが何ダース<span class="vocab">寄った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>寄</rb><rt>よ</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;approach; draw near</span></span>って、これほど<span class="vocab">立派な<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>立派</rb><rt>りっぱ</rt></ruby>な&nbsp;splendid</span></span><span class="vocab">旦那様<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>旦那様</rb><rt>だんなさま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;husband</span></span>が出来るもんか。</p>

